@node "feedback" "Feedback"

This program is not at all perfect in that it's algorithm could probably be
more efficient (faster). And it would be possible to make it handle objects
with sharp edges etc. Also points that have many adges will not be removed in
this version, I will have to invent a whole new (generic) algorithm to solve
this. Any future versions depend upon you, finding bugs, having neat ideas or
generally showing enough interest. Hope you like it, let me know what you
think.

